verbose_text: 25 To date, several other biomarkers such as microalbumin, N-acetyl-B-D-glucosaminidase, kidney injury molecule-1, interleukin-18, liver fatty acid binding protein, netrins and nestin have been studied for the diagnosis, severity classification and most importantly, the modification of the outcome in AKI.
